For Apple Watch Series 7 45mm Stylish Rhinestone Electroplating Rhombus Imprint Hard PC Case with Tempered Glass Screen Protector - Black

Hard PC case with built-in tempered glass screen protector covers the watch screen and curved edges for 360-degree full protection for your watch.

    The outside of this watch case is made of PC material, comfortable and smooth to the touch

    With electroplating design, fashionable and stylish

    Practical design allows access to all controls, buttons, sensors, and features

    Accurate cutouts of cover shell fit your watch perfectly

    Comes with a tempered glass screen protector that offers external surface protection to your watch

    Ultra-thin tempered glass film can make the content of the watch quick response

    Easy to install for its snap-on design to avoid taking the straps off first

Specification:

    Material: PC + tempered glass

    Size: 50 x 41.5mm

    Weight: 12g

Compatible with:

    Apple Watch Series 7 45mm

Package included:

    1 x Hard PC Case with Tempered Glass Screen Protector
    Other items not included
